data.title: LIVING IN STEREO - 90s To Now Experience
data.meta_description: Contact LIVING IN STEREO - 90s To Now Experience from Mission Viejo on The Bash. Browse Top 40 Band prices, photos, and 1 reviews, with a rating of 5 out of 5.
data.text: WANT 90s TO NOW FUN? STYLE? ENERGY? DANCING? LOOK NO FURTHER! That’s what a LIVING IN STEREO event is all about! LIS features dynamic powerhouse male & female lead vocalists to offer a robust song selection. Whether busting out the best 90s pop, rock or dance hits, getting creative with medleys and mashups, or changing things up with a tasty new-school dance jam, LIS has a big sound and huge presence - a true crowd pleaser. We refer to our show as The 90's To Now Experience - a full package of dance & rock music for everyone. Born to entertain, the members of this band don’t just stand there and regurgitate covers; they deliver each musical tribute with passion and conviction. LIVING IN STEREO specializes in weddings, special events, corporate events, private parties and summer concerts, but are also available for venues and public events. We're courteous, easy to work with, punctual professionals whose goal is ensure you get the absolute best out of your event! We also come fully equipped with a state-of-the-art QSC sound system and full lighting rig (if needed).
